PrecisRe-appointment of the HONOURABLE CLAUDE BISSON, of Montreal, Quebec, as a commissioner to review the activities of the Communications Security Establishment for the purpose of determining whether those activities are in compliance with the law, for a period of three years, effective June 19, 1999.
